Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小孩竟然把我家的佑…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 在吵什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 这不是美有树吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了呢 怎么了 这么早来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 把佑还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在这里吗 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树 难得来一趟 上来坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有那个空闲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把佑带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 美有树急性子的地方一点都没变呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 你就上来坐一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 拿双拖鞋出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}\N 穿\N \N越 \N \N时 \N \N空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥…你一定要保护好遥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么我必须要被你说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你…就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆 安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是好久了呢 美有树到我们家来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去可是一直来玩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一起来喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在这种时候才好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是很好喝的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天要喝个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说些什么啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你这个地方一点都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 我看上去有那么年轻么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了庆祝和旧友的再会 来干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 要去告诉佑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来 巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得吓唬小孩子很有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃的话就一定会输
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不愿意输的话就战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抱有战斗的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 怎么办啊 被阿姨知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算像这样一直藏起来 总有一天还是会被找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去管他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙还不会去体会他人的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦是未来的佑的话 告诉他怎么做不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是我的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是自己去尝试并克服就没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么那样…太无情了 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种家伙说的话 根本不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这没志气的样子算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有骨气的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以为自己是大人就了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种家伙才不是我的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一点都不了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 和佑之间发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也不是什么了不起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 让他暂时在我们家里玩一段时间好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行 那孩子还有考试要参加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是最重要的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那种口气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是把我当作那种强迫自己小孩参加考试的笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从以前开始就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把我当笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么都不和我商量一下就决定了大学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你不是去了东京的美大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 合格的时候不是好好的和你解释过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去东京的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐要去早锻炼 先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的姐姐 原本应该去东京的大学的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要代替她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 妈妈却不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈一直很喜欢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起一事无成的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:07:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说我和死去的大阿姨很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以努力学习的话 一定能进好的中学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是绝对要考进才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 再倒一杯给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是喝的太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 因为真的很好喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑是个非常乖巧的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能成为像惠美姐姐一样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香也是这么认为的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的佑可以成为像惠美姐那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部洒出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我家的钢琴上还放着照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那些里面 有我妈妈中学时候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和大阿姨一起拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经问过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把这个摆出来装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后妈妈她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠美姐姐他头脑聪明 运动万能 什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开朗 有很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以佑一定可以成为像姐姐那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起哦 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦 我去买酒回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把我和大阿姨做比较呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见都没有见过大阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在二年前外婆死了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈开始和我说起大阿姨的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们去问一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问为什么佑的妈妈要把佑和自己的姐姐做比较
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢 去问那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要好好的问清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手啦 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠美姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 我们有事要问您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点和我一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不听你的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 这事和你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把佑和阿姨的姐姐做比较呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且阿姨你 二年前从来没有和佑说过那种话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 那是从札幌的外婆的葬礼后开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会代替姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空在歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 遥 你们在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个椅子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 妈妈出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧 美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝果汁吗 美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想离家出走的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是因为相信你 才把你叫到我家来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离家出走说起来简单 可你有好好计划过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我把存的钱都带上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 中学生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香和我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑的妈妈 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 妈妈消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与不同的时空接触了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的思想有的时候会给时空带来影响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的思想？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成宇宙中所有物质的量子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的思想有时会产生干涉它的力场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是最喜欢姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑好 又开朗 还那么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我能代替她死去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也是认为那样比较好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不能这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为比起我…妈妈…更加喜欢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈只一味注视着死去的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是 比起我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨现在在哪里啊 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不同的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拥有她无法忘却的思念的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念的时空？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在过去 在过去的某个时空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是因为我的力量造成这样的后果的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把她带回来也是可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要确定她转移的时空不是一件容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无限扩展的时空中寻找一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同在沙滩上寻找掉落的一根针一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥的话应该能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候你也改变了时空的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个时候的事情我已经记不太清了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:15:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话 一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信它吧 相信自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不行 不能顺利进行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己 你一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不感受到阿姨的想法就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 我去下面试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得要那样才会更加接近阿姨的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去感觉就可以了 去感觉阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树如果离家出走的话 伯父伯母一定会很担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我想成为像姐姐一样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像姐姐一样被周围人所爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是想离家出走什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想引起妈妈的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是乘缆车翻过山就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妈妈 也没有担心我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能稍微离我远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 让佑的妈妈回到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的美有树不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行包也不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树在我家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想已经和明日香一起睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真是的…让我那么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在担心我吗 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年 那孩子的姐姐因为交通事故去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那孩子也不在了的话 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 所以就不要太责备她了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就做那孩子喜欢的汉堡肉饼等她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢汉堡肉饼的是惠美姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 只要是妈妈亲手做的料理都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树已经睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方睡着的话会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快起来 美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 佑 在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:21:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道已经和你妈妈见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 美有树 去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在沙发上睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是母子么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈睡着了么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈还想再在这里坐一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想和遥的妈妈再聊一会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒…要消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.12,0:24:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.11,0:24:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏日的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.11,0:24:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年后会怎么样啊 你说出来看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.40,0:24:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再妨碍我的话 就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.73,0:25:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.93,0:25:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 暴风雨的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.43,0:25:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候能告诉我吗


